# fuelsdk-node


## Available objects in this version:

* Campaign
* Campaign Asset
* Content Area
* Data Extension
* Data Extension Column
* Data Extension Row
* Email
* Folder
* List
* List Subscriber
* Subscriber
* Triggered Send
* Bounce Event
* Click Event
* Open Event
* Sent Event
* Unsub Event
* SOAP
* REST


## Usage:

See https://github.com/salesforcefuel/node-sdk-backbone-app for examples.
